<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Miscall" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Miscall,</orth> to call by a wrong name, to name improperly: <cit><quote>simple truth --ed simplicity,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 66.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 66, 11</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>my heart will sigh when I m. it so,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 1.3.263" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 3, 263</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>thou dost m. retire,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 5.4.21" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 4, 21</bibl></cit>.
